{"id": 2582, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于如何回应“你为什么不说话”，你都有哪些心得？", "description": "来，我们自制一份社恐患者求生指南。（题图来自：iStock ©️ drante）", "record_count": 2227, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2018102215432771pjQkyBDE4Pi3rz.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-10-25T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 306944, "content": "累", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1441848}, {"id": 307200, "content": "我在听你说", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483733}, {"id": 306689, "content": "本想说“因为话不投机半句多”，然而半句都多干嘛说一句，于是继续沉默。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423794}, {"id": 307201, "content": "我在听你说", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483733}, {"id": 307713, "content": "不想说→_→", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1475269}, {"id": 306690, "content": "微笑 回应说在想一些事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1480727}, {"id": 307202, "content": "“我有语言洁癖。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1128374}, {"id": 306691, "content": "说点什么…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1431819}, {"id": 306692, "content": "我觉得大家讲的都很好，我没什么需要补充的了……\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050868}, {"id": 307460, "content": "我怕我说了 你会没话说", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1485181}, {"id": 307716, "content": "我大概只有心情不好才会不说话吧😄", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 347171}, {"id": 311302, "content": "我在打盹", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1182031}, {"id": 306695, "content": "祸从口出", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377387}, {"id": 308231, "content": "懒得不想说话", "image": "img/option/option/20181101234132UGIrJ4fF6tHWBe09.jpg", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 569294}, {"id": 308487, "content": "现在越来越多人在📱上“说话”，不独我一人\n对方不说话，我也不好开口……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1490698}, {"id": 306697, "content": "闭嘴，闭眼，用心感受", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1372202}, {"id": 306953, "content": "瞧您说的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1443676}, {"id": 307209, "content": "啊～没有啊～你说的挺好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1397342}, {"id": 306698, "content": "也没什么，就是懒得动嘴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482035}, {"id": 306699, "content": "继续不说话\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482041}, {"id": 306700, "content": "不是一个物种怎么交流？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482048}, {"id": 306703, "content": "对方反反复复反反复复发作时的症状是由于时间原因造成皮肤的新陈代谢产生反应就是我自己想办法让你知道自己有能力和美关系需要什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 572666}, {"id": 306705, "content": "我是不是你最疼爱的人？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879653}, {"id": 306961, "content": "没有心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1464527}, {"id": 306707, "content": "我在听，先了解一下", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1063169}, {"id": 306708, "content": "不想", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 307221, "content": "你说的比较有趣呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483861}, {"id": 306710, "content": "您先说", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1462146}, {"id": 307222, "content": "一个字五毛钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1362070}, {"id": 306711, "content": "在图书馆你要说什么😌", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1000549}, {"id": 308760, "content": "你希望我对你说什么呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335130}, {"id": 306713, "content": "就是不知道说啥啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482092}, {"id": 307738, "content": "和我以后都没有什么交集的人，也没有什么沟通的必要", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1297840}, {"id": 306715, "content": "脸上笑嘻嘻 内心mmp", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1180833}, {"id": 306971, "content": "我可能会回答 我也不知道，然后这个天就被我聊死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482850}, {"id": 306716, "content": "可能是有点饿了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470846}, {"id": 306972, "content": "因为我觉得我不说你也懂啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1479222}, {"id": 306717, "content": "老了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482104}, {"id": 307231, "content": "我在听你说话啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1463681}, {"id": 306720, "content": "告，告辞！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1476450}, {"id": 306976, "content": "无话可说", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1482854}, {"id": 306721, "content": "对方表示不想和你说话，并且扔了你一只拖鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992056}, {"id": 307233, "content": "因为我在和别人说话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1483906}, {"id": 306723, "content": "好尬", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449386}, {"id": 306979, "content": "还是手机里内容的有意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450591}, {"id": 306724, "content": "不想说话，和怕说错话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470426}, {"id": 306725, "content": "刚刚搞错了不过答案是一样的，\n不想说话/怕说错话", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470426}, {"id": 306726, "content": "生活是天籁，需要静心聆听", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867637}, {"id": 306727, "content": "说了，只是不想和你说。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1093036}, {"id": 306728, "content": "啊？哦。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1450397}]}